description:
Take advantage of this incredible development opportunity located in a premier location and approximately 100m to the spectacular Tanilba Bay beach.


Positioned on an approximate 1024m2 corner block of land, there is an abundance of space for any future plans of expansion or simply building your own dream home to embrace the stunning water views at your fingertips (STCA).


Home to a two-story cottage with three bedrooms of accommodation, a fantastic outdoor entertaining balcony as well as a double lock up garage, this property makes for the ideal investment.


Sitting on a huge corner block, take advantage of the great potential for subdivision using both Victory View and President Poincare Parade (STCA).


You will have the best of both worlds being within close proximity to the Tanilba Bay town center, the waterfront, as well as an approximate 20 minute drive to the Newcastle Airport, you are spoilt for choice as far as location goes.


If you have been searching for your next project, development, or a site to build your dream home, do not hesitate in contacting Rebecca Dean 0421 169 922 or Regan Blanch 0481 996 678 to arrange your own private inspection.
